{
  "stem": "10588.6",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The first block when I came was, was a, a woman from Czechoslovakia, and her name was Olga on block 8.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Later, when I was in the [NON-ENGLISH], I was in another block.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I no longer remember the name of it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But this [INAUDIBLE] I worked to the end.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- so when we worked there, if we could, we used, you know, to damage some of the clothes because we knew that this going to go for the, for the Germans, you know.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was very humiliating to work there because it's very hard for me to talk about it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I will tell you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "As I said, I was brought up very modest.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We knew very little about sex.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Nobody told us at home about sex or anything else.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I never was-- till I was married, I was never sexually active.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I didn't know anything about sex.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I was never a normal teenager.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "My teenage years was in the concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "In the ghetto, I was deprived of going to school, of, of going to proms, all the things that normal teenagers do.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when we would leave, they'd search us inwardly.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If we didn't, because sometimes you would find in the clothes something.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they want to make sure that we didn't smuggle out any, any gold or anything else.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And each time they made this examination, I feel like I'm dying inside.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I felt so humiliated, so-- but what helped me a lot under those moments, believe it or not, I remembered my mother's words when I had the encounter.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Itkalo, your menschlichkeit does not depend on how others treat you, but on how you treat others.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I would say, well, I'm not doing it to them, they're doing it to me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So this way, I didn't lose my self-worth, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was painful, emotionally very painful a lot of times.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So working-- Were people able to smuggle stuff out of Kanada or no?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I hardly believe so because they searched us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They searched us in, in private places.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Can you imagine the humiliation and pain?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So it was-- one thing that was good though that was our advantage, was both painful and was to our advantage, is that because it was [NON-ENGLISH] Hitler said that they are the superior race, and we're the inferior.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the Gypsies, too, they said they inferior.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were Gypsies, but not in the same-- the Jewish people, the Jewish girls were separate.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was never with men.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was never with any other group.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were other groups, too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were Jehovah Witness.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were Gypsies.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There were political.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There were homosexuals.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But we were not together with them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Every group had different, different places.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So because of the [INAUDIBLE] that-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's just so overwhelming when I start thinking about all, all the horrible thing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And one of the things which also-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] whenever I found out that they-- see, they had a live orchestra.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Jewish people played live orchestra.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And whenever a transport came, a new transport arrived and they were making the selection and burning people, the music played.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Many times-- for a long time, when I would hear music, I started to cry.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "People wouldn't understand why.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I love music.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You can see I have lots of tapes and things, but-- because I always remembered the barbarism.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Can you imagine killing people and music playing?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And with Mengele and with other nurses who were giving injection for Jew because it wasn't always the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was told, this I didn't experience, because when I came, unfortunately they had the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But before, they used the gas vents.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They gave injections, you know, in, in the heart.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, so the point is that when I think to myself, this was the most educated people, professors, college graduates.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So what was wrong?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was told that education, the importance of education, the People of the Book from, from-- my, my great grandfather was a scholar of, of-- my, my grandmother, my grandparents.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And here, what did they do with the books?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't have electricity.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I had to go in with a candle down to the root cellar, but I had the love and the support.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So that's when I started to compare the values with everything.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I realized once something very important, very important-- that everybody is human.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But not everybody's humane.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that menchlichkeit is the highest form of religion, education, and achievement because without it, everything fails.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Knowledge is never wrong in itself, it's how you use it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I didn't stop craving knowledge.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But I started to-- I said, how do I know people now?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "How can I tell?",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
